Class Ip4Prefix

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip4.Ip4Prefix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Ip4Prefix
extends java.lang.Object
implements IpPrefix
    Internet Protocol version 4 (IPv4) network prefix.

    Only prefix bits can be non-zeros.
